245
00:16:32,790 --> 00:16:34,550
Tak z čeho máš strach?

246
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,080
Propánakrále.

247
00:16:38,160 --> 00:16:39,920
Už jsi dospělá.

248
00:16:42,600 --> 00:16:43,770
A

249
00:16:43,770 --> 00:16:46,770
