293
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,470
Hej, nech ho.

294
00:19:27,470 --> 00:19:28,660
Jae Min

295
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,560
selhal u dalšího konkurzu.

296
00:19:32,270 --> 00:19:34,090
