421
00:29:46,820 --> 00:29:47,940
Počkej...

422
00:30:19,490 --> 00:30:20,600
Co to je?

423
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:26,410
Pane řediteli?

424
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,350
Co tu děláte?

425
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,610
Cože?

426
00:30:37,470 --> 00:30:38,580
Omlouvám se.

427
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:40,860
- Slečno Gil. 
- Ano?

428
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:43,740
Co je to za papírky?

429
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:48,330
Tyhle?

430
00:30:50,050 --> 00:30:51,900
To jsou

431
00:30:52,050 --> 00:30:54,920
odmašťující papírky.

432
00:30:57,320 --> 00:30:58,510
Odmašťující?

433
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:02,120
Vidíte? 
Tohle

434
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:05,290
